</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-03-02-0031-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-03-03-02-0031-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>A note at the end of the letter-book copy in <span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ U.S. Library of Congress, George Washington Papers, Washington, D.C. ]">DLC:GW</span> reads Boxes of lead 19 &amp;  abt 270 each.</p>

</div>
